							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-lg-2 appear-animation" data-appear-animation="fadeIn" data-appear-animation-delay="500">
						<a href="/iletisim" class="btn btn-modern btn-dark mt-1">Hızlı Teklif İçin Buraya Tıklayın!</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="row">
					<div class="col py-3">
						<hr class="solid mt-5 mb-2">
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="row">
